  "title": "Kitchen Crew (AWS of up to 2 month salary/Multiple Locations/Choose your own shift)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Kitchen Crew</strong><br /><strong>Salary:</strong> <strong>$2,550 – $2,750</strong><br /><strong>📍Location:</strong> Bukit Panjang/Kent Ridge/Orchard/Serangoon/Bugis/Lavender/Lentor</p><p>Join a growing F&B brand and be part of a dynamic kitchen team with attractive incentives and clear progression.</p><h3><strong>✨Job Highlights</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>2 days paid trial</strong><br /><em>(If performance is good, enjoy a </em><em><strong>$200 salary increment</strong></em><em>)</em></li><li>Choice of working location</li><li>Medical consultation fees claimable</li><li><strong>Monthly attendance incentive:</strong> $50<br /><em>(No unpaid leave / MC)</em></li><li><strong>Performance bonus & annual increment</strong><br /><em>(After 1 year of service, up to </em><em><strong>2 months’ salary</strong></em><em>)</em></li><li>Lunch provided</li></ul><h3><strong>👩‍🍳Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Prepare the kitchen and restaurant for daily opening and closing operations.</li><li>Sort, prepare, and assemble orders according to kitchen SOPs.</li><li>Operate various cooking stations, including:Deep fryerWater boilerInduction cooking station</li><li>Maintain a clean, organised, and safe kitchen environment in compliance with hygiene and safety standards.</li><li>Monitor inventory levels of ingredients and supplies and place orders to prevent shortages.</li><li>Support team members to ensure smooth kitchen operations.</li></ul><h3><strong>⏰ Working Schedule</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>5 / 5.5 / 6 days work week</strong> (choice available)</li><li><strong>Working hours:</strong> 10 hours per shift</li><li><strong>Break:</strong> 1 hour 30 minutes</li><li><strong>Lunch provided</strong></li></ul><h3><strong>✅ Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>Able to work in a fast-paced kitchen environment.</li><li>Able to stand for long hours.</li><li>Willing to follow kitchen SOPs and hygiene standards.</li><li>Team player with a positive attitude.</li><li>Prior kitchen or F&B experience is an advantage but not required.</li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>Apply now for a quicker response.<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><strong>K. Keshika Samantha (R26159509)</strong><br />Just Recruit Singapore Pte Ltd (EA12C6295)</p>",
